    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=You are an invoice data extraction specialist.\n\nExtract the following fields from the invoice \ntext below.\n\nFields to extract:\n- invoice_number\n- invoice_date\n- due_date\n- vendor_name\n- vendor_address\n- client_name\n- client_address\n- subtotal\n- tax_amount\n- total_amount\n- payment_method\n\nRules:\n- If a field is not found return null for that field\n- Return amounts as numbers only, no currency symbols\n- Return dates in YYYY-MM-DD format\n- Return ONLY valid JSON, no markdown, no explanation\n\nExample output:\n{\n  \"invoice_number\": \"INV-2024-0042\",\n  \"invoice_date\": \"2024-06-15\",\n  \"due_date\": \"2024-07-15\",\n  \"vendor_name\": \"ABC Supplies Co.\",\n  \"vendor_address\": \"123 Business Street, Manila\",\n  \"client_name\": \"XYZ Corporation\",\n  \"client_address\": \"456 Client Avenue, Cebu\",\n  \"subtotal\": 2200.00,\n  \"tax_amount\": 264.00,\n  \"total_amount\": 2464.00,\n  \"payment_method\": \"Bank Transfer\"\n}\n\nInvoice Text:\n{{ $json.text }}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.agent",
      "typeVersion": 3.1,
      "position": [
